    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育平台学生端的状态流转图。核心是学生数据库和教育内容CDN之间的连接状态变化。起点应该是从StudentDB开始建立连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Connecting"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以StudentDB触发Connecting状态，然后Connecting会同时指向ContentCDN和Connected对吗？还是说Connecting到CDN是独立的路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connecting",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Connecting状态会尝试拉取CDN资源，同时成功后进入Connected。所以Connecting要分出两条线：一条到ContentCDN表示资源请求，一条到Connected表示连接就绪。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connecting",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，StudentDB到Connecting，Connecting分别到ContentCDN和Connected，这部分我先画上了。Connected之后应该进入什么状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Connecting",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Connected之后进入Idle空闲状态。从Idle可以进入Sending发送数据，或者超时进入Timeout，也可以直接关闭连接进入Closed。Sending完成后要回到Idle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connected",
        "Idle",
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "Closed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Sending和Timeout之间有关系吗？另外Closed之后还有后续状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "Closed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Sending过程中也可能超时，所以Sending要连到Timeout。Timeout之后需要重新请求CDN资源，所以Timeout要回到ContentCDN。Closed是终态，但关闭前如果缓存失效也要回CDN刷新，所以Closed也连到ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "Closed",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程：StudentDB启动Connecting，连接CDN并进入Connected，然后Idle循环处理Sending，异常时走Timeout重连CDN，正常关闭时走Closed并在需要时回CDN。所有状态都画好了。",
